        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/arab-leaders-emergency-summit-egypt-new-administrative-capital.png" alt="Arab leaders pose during the emergency Arab summit at Egypt's New Administrative Capital" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
